00030 float liftracc_sdsdot(const int n, const float alpha, const float * x, const int incx, const float * y, const int incy)
00031 {
00032 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 1
00033     liftracc_function_timing_start(&(liftracc_function_profiling_data[LIFTRACC_FUNCTION_SDSDOT]));
00034 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ */
00035     float (*liftracc_plugin_func)();
00036     float ret = 0.0;
00037    
00038 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 2
00039     liftracc_function_timing_start(&(liftracc_profiling_data[SELECT_CALL]));
00040 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_  */
00041 
00042 #ifdef _LIFTRACC_SELECTOR_NEW_
00043 
00044     pinfo.info1 = n;
00045 
00046     *(void **) (&liftracc_plugin_func) = liftracc_selector_select(SELECT_SDSDOT, &pinfo);
00047 #else
00048     *(void **) (&liftracc_plugin_func) = liftracc_selector_select("liftracc_plugin_sdsdot");
00049 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_SELECTOR_NEW_ */
00050 
00051 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 2
00052     liftracc_function_timing_stop(&(liftracc_profiling_data[SELECT_CALL]));
00053 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_  */
00054 
00055     if (liftracc_plugin_func != 0)  {
00056         ret = (*liftracc_plugin_func)(n, alpha, x, incx, y, incy);
00057     } else
00058         ERROR("liftracc_sdsdot not executed");
00059 
00060 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 1
00061     liftracc_function_timing_stop(&(liftracc_function_profiling_data[LIFTRACC_FUNCTION_SDSDOT]));
00062 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ */
00063 
00064     return ret;
00065 }
